<h2 class="bold font-l">Demise curse</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
After his defeat, Demise curses the first Link so his descendants must forever fight an incarnation of his hatred (Ganondorf). </p>
<p class='example_row'>Example of:<br><a href="/pmwiki/pmwiki.php/Main/DyingCurse" class='trope-example-link'>Dying Curse</a></p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="alt-titles section section-fact">
<h3>
<strong>Alternative Title(s):</strong>
<span>Skyward Sword</span> </h3>
</div>
